Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.33,0:00:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽過很多關于世界毀滅時的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've heard a lot of stories about when the world fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.75,0:00:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死人多于活人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There were more dead than the living,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界好像開始會變冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it started to look like the world would go cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就快了 差不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It felt like it was almost there. Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人通過相互聯系而幸存下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some people survived by connecting with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Making found families.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人屈服于黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Others gave in to the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是很久以前的事了 現在還是 明天也是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was a long time ago. And it's now. Will it be tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-安全 -安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Clear. - Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分散 檢查每個窗戶 門口 樓梯和走廊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fan out. Check every window, doorway, stairway and hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-在此終結 -你覺得他們有多少人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This ends here. - How many you think they got?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系 把他們一個接一個地干掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't matter. Gonna take them out one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看我們找到了誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look who we found.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-赫歇爾呢  -他和以利亞還有其他人在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where's Hershel? - He's with Elijah and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他很隱蔽也很安全 -他很好 瑪吉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's hidden and safe. - He's good, Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是來干掉軍團的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're here to take out shithead and the dickless brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我一直說的 我們應該先回聯邦社區\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like I've been saying, we should go back to the Commonwealth first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.06,0:01:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們的人帶出來 然后一起對付霍恩斯比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get our people out and then deal with Hornsby together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 加貝 他可能已經用無線電報信了 你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Gabe, he probably already radioed back. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 他認識我們 我們沒法通過這些檢查站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, he knows us. We're never getting through those checkpoints.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他在讓他的人 追捕我們的家人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if he has his people go after our families in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:02:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡羅爾在那兒 羅西塔 杰瑞 以西結也在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Carol's there. So is Rosita and Jerry, Ezekiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-希望他們能應付得來 -希望不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We have hope they can handle it. - Hope is running low.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這里辯論的時間越長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the longer we're out here having these debates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在家的家人面臨的風險越大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the more our families back home are at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的人也在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our people are out here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要在霍恩斯比抓住任何人之前 找到他并把他殺死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to find Hornsby and kill him before he gets to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, wait. Hold up. Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以做到所有這一切 他們以前從未見過你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can do all of this. They've never seen your face before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說我直接闖進去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you saying I just walk right on in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我就是這個意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. That's exactly what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我也去 -不 安妮 你不能跟來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Me too. - No, Annie, not you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們中只有一人需要進入敵人的內部 嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only one of us needs to go into the belly of the beast. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了 不管怎樣 我都得完蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Besides, I am fucked either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我不會那么容易被干掉的 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, you're not gonna get rid of me that easy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 計劃是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. So what's the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答 這是布拉沃隊 我們需要清理第四象限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in. This is Bravo team. We need to clear out quadrant four.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-收到 布拉沃 -開始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Copy that, Bravo. - Let's roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我們來了結這一切吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\t(\fs18)\fscx290\fscy380\move(192,45,192,55)\c&Hddeeff&\b1\fn微軟雅黑\bord0\fad(200,800)\alpha&H60&}行尸走肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\t(\fs18)\fscx70\move(112,180,119,178)\c&Hddeeff&\b0\fn微軟雅黑\bord0\fad(200,800)\alpha&H70&}第十一季  第十七集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外掛字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}風吹來的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  雙語合并
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人盯著那輛該死的車嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does anyone have eyes on that goddamn car?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動 我們需要向聯邦傳達信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fire it up. We need to get a message to the Commonwealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得信號不夠強\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think the signal is strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即撥打\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dial in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡爾霍恩 說話 你能收到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Calhoun. Calhoun. Come in. Do you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對達里爾迪克森 亞倫實行應急規程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Contingency protocol on Daryl Dixon. Aaron...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 搜索信號 然后給家里發信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, go find a goddamn signal and get a message home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那輛車出現 確保我們的人已經做好準備\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If that car shows up, make sure our people are on the wall, ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是的 長官 -開槍射殺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes, sir. - Shoot to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們看到被盜車輛向西行駛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have visual on the stolen vehicle heading westbound.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:06:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-兩分鐘后開始攔截 -把它拿下 然后找到剩下的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Moving to intercept, two minutes. - Take it down, then find the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果米爾頓或默瑟知道了 我們就完蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If this gets back to Milton or Mercer, we're eighty-sixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在要阻止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We contain this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標西行 保持穩定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Target westbound. Keep it steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊 目標在往北行駛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold on. Target is now northbound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持穩定 我們幾乎追上他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep it steady. We almost got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試著在前面切斷他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Try and cut him off up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要公正 交出塞巴斯蒂安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want justice. Deliver Sebastian now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要公正 交出塞巴斯蒂安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want justice. Deliver Sebastian now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要公正 交出塞巴斯蒂安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want justice. Deliver Sebastian now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要公正 交出塞巴斯蒂安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want justice. Deliver Sebastian now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要公正 交出塞巴斯蒂安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want justice. Deliver Sebastian now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要公正\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦社區的公民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Citizens of the Commonwealth,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你們的州長 帕梅拉米爾頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this is your governor, Pamela Milton.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你們都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I want you all to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個所謂的報道不過是謊言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this so-called report is nothing but lies
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意在向受夠了苦難的人們傳播恐懼和憤怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}meant to sow fear and anger in people who have suffered enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們要公正 -但我了解我的兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We want justice. - But I know my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能做出他被指控的那些可怕的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He couldn't have done the horrible things he's been accused of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要公正\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他是個不錯的年輕人 -交出塞巴斯蒂安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He is a good young man. - Deliver Sebastian now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要公正\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們想要的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the Commonwealth is his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦社區是他的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是變革的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出塞巴斯蒂安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deliver Sebastian now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要堅持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他絕不會做任何破壞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He would never do anything to undermine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們偉大社區...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the safety and stability...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有人下落不明 他們在某個地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-...of our great community.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- ...安全性和穩定性的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們要公正 -這可能會有危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We want justice. - This could get ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果事態變糟 我們需要準備好幫助這些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to be ready to help these people if it goes sideways.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況變得更糟只是時間問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's only a matter of time until this gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們需要各種方案 -你的意思是離開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We need options. - What you mean, leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不想離開 這些人需要我們的幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I don't wanna leave. These people need our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在每個人都回來之前 我們不要做任何決定 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing gets decided until everyone's back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護車站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Secure the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要公正 交出塞巴斯蒂安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want justice. Deliver Sebastian now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要公正\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一種榮譽和特權\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That calling is an honor and a privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他在里面 把他交出來 -交出塞巴斯蒂安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's in there. Bring him out. - Deliver Sebastian now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你為什么沒穿制服  -休假\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What are you doing out of uniform? - Personal day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不行 不能在這種情況下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not today. Not with all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我的問題 也不是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't my problem. It's not yours either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默瑟上將 長官 有事需要你盡快處理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}General Mercer, sir. You're needed in processing, ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會想看這個的 長官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're gonna want to see this one, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我這就來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天需要你 這些人需要你 現在去換制服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you today. These people do. Now suit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要公正\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快會找到真正的肇事者 并將他們繩之以法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon I will find the real culprits and bring them to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面我將回答一些公民提出的書面問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I will answer some written questions submitted by citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得她知道他在哪里嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think she knows where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可能躲起來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Probably in hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那些人 他更害怕她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's more afraid of her than he is of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你還好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-“你在怎樣找他 ” -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-"What are you doing to find him?" - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在跟蹤多個線索 并且不會停止...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are following multiple leads and will not stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想繼續\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanna keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就繼續\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在努力尋找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are working diligently to find the people responsible for
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散布這些謊言的人 請放心 他們一定會被繩之以法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}spreading these lies. Rest assured, they will be brought to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 在荒地上聽說過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, word gets around the wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不認識\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個朋友告訴我關于你的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A friend told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我來找她時應該找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Said that I should ask for you when I came looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃普麗爾 當我來找埃普麗爾的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}April. When I came looking for April.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她發生了什么事嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know what happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我這個就表示不是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you asking me that means that it can't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來這里的真正原因是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you really here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到了一些麻煩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I ran into some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個穿襯衫打領帶的混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some shirt-and-tie-wearing shit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他一起做事的走狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and his clamshell assholes he runs with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他點水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get him some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好的 誰派你來的  -我想你知道是誰派我來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right. Who sent you? - I think you know who sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達里爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 聽著 霍恩斯比這個混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, listen. So, this Hornsby prick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直在追殺我們 我們在處理這個情況\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's been cutting us up out there, and we're dealing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 問題是這里也有我們需要保護的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, see, the problem is that we got people in here to protect too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但我還是被派到這里來了 -我不能讓你隨便就進來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And yet I was sent here anyway. - I can't just let you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們這里有規則 -規則 對啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We got rules here. - Rules. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 如果其他人都不遵守這些規則 那你為什么要遵守呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if no else is playing by those rules, then why are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡羅爾阿姨 藍莓煎餅要燒焦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Aunt Carol? - Hmm? The blueberry pancakes are burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 你不喜歡燒焦的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh. Oh, no. You don't like them burned?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不 -你錯過美味了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not really. You're missing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是凱利拍的 為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Kelly took these? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們可以了解這個地方 留意事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we can learn about this place. Keep an eye on things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞倫叔叔和達里爾叔叔什么時候回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When are Uncle Aaron and Uncle Daryl coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你更喜歡他們做的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, you like their cooking better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么會 除非有篝火 否則達里爾不知道他在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No way. Unless there's a campfire, Daryl has no idea what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸無論在哪里都能做出好吃的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My dad's a good cook wherever he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們很快就會回來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么了  -也許沒什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What is it? - Maybe nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你們起來 我們得離開這\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. You guys get up. We got to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過早餐...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們稍后會回來 現在我們必須躲起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, we'll come back later. Right now we got to play the quiet game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人 你確定他沒說別的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's empty. Are you sure he didn't say anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只出現了迪克森的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dixon was the only name that came through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去學校檢查一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's check the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄 什么鬼 你在這里做什么 伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dude. What the hell? What are you doing here, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來救你們的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm here to save your asses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡羅爾在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is Carol?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理威士忌艾克丘爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charlie Whiskey Actual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理威士忌艾克丘爾 這是外勤隊布拉沃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charlie Whiskey Actual, this is field unit Bravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理威士忌艾克丘爾 這是外勤隊布拉沃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charlie Whiskey Actual. Charlie Whiskey Actual, this is field unit Bravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 這是艾克丘爾 請說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Copy. This is Actual. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丘爾 這是外勤隊布拉沃 OTB\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Actual, this is field unit Bravo OTB.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如下是來自霍恩斯比的訊息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Message from Hornsby, as follows...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外勤隊 再說一遍 我沒收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Field unit, come back. I didn't get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們今天要來個小冒險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're just gonna have a little adventure today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你們回臥室等著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you guys to go back to the bedroom and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我叫你們之前不要出來 去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And don't come out until I call. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡羅爾 安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Carol, it's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實證明你可能是對的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Turns out you might have been right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能應該呆在那該死的小屋里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I probably should've stayed in the goddamn cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍恩斯比試圖通過審問赫歇爾來驚嚇瑪吉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hornsby tried to scare Maggie by interrogating Hershel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們猜他會以某種方式嘗試\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So the thought is that he is somehow gonna try
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用孩子們把我們的人引出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to use the kids to draw our people out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他們來找達里爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's why they came for Daryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果霍恩斯比派了剛才那兩個 他一直在秘密進行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if Hornsby sent those two, he's keeping it under the radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這意味著我們可能在他們之前找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which means we might be able to get ahead of them. And him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰瑞 你還能進入那個閣樓空間嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jerry, do you still have access to that attic space?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 女士 如你所要求的 備有供應品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, ma'am. Stocked with supplies, like you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把孩子們帶去那里 然后告訴其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep the kids there, and get word to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們準備好 收到你的信號就行動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell them to be ready to move on your signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我會開始步驟 -準備好做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'll start the chain. - Ready for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里似乎不是那種\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, this doesn't seem like the kind of place
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以牽著手隨意走出前門的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you can just stroll out the front gate hand in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我和你要去試著獲得一些保障\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's why me and you are gonna go try to get some insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她來了 在那邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There she is. Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的女兒死了 你打算怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our daughter's dead. What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法想象你們所經歷的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't imagine the pain you've experienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也感到恐懼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I share your horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我無法帶回你們所愛之人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Though I can't bring your loved ones back,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我會對發生的事追查到底\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will get to the bottom of what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到肇事者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and who was responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道是誰干的 是他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We know who did this. He did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你把你兒子藏在哪里了  -你們讀到的不是事實\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where are you hiding your son? - What you read was not the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你知道他在哪 -好吧 夠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You know where he is. - All right. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退后 馬上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get back. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然呢 你會讓我們也消失嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or what? You gonna disappear us too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嘿 我們理解你們的心情 真的 -冷靜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey. We hear you. We do. - Calm down.
