Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友康妮 那個記者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your friend, Connie, the journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得她會知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't suppose she would have an idea
