Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞巴斯蒂安在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's Sebastian?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要塞巴斯蒂安 帕梅拉 他在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}MAN 2: We want Sebastian. Pamela, where is he?
