Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上行動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么意思 帕梅拉知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean, Pamela knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷疑 你知道 至少是懷疑 誰是這篇文章的幕后黑手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, suspects, you know, at least, who's behind the article.
