Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告訴康妮了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you told Connie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很想先和你談談\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I really wanted to talk to you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你知道她的性格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you know what she's like.
