Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始 你就已經看到了 這個地方的本質\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From the beginning, you've seen this place for what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從不支持胡編亂造 這是你更好的品質之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've never stood for bullshit. It's one of your better qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你比誰都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you know more than anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道什么時候該離開 這讓我們度過了很多難關\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we've made it through a lot by knowing when it's good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這里的情況變糟 我想為你們制定 一個可靠的撤離計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if things go bad here, I want a strong exit plan for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:21:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“你們”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"You guys"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 麥格納 你知道我不能丟下托米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Magna. You know I can't leave Tomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你 我們哪兒也不去 就是這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't go anywhere without you. End of story.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不 麥格納 那不是... -美子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, Magna. That's not... - Miko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.41,0:22:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果到時間離開了 那么我們就都走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the time comes to go, then we're all going,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.83,0:22:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我必須拖著你和托米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even if I have to drag you and Tomi along.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.58,0:22:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 我們會保持警惕 盡我們所能幫助每一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until then, we keep our eyes peeled, help everyone we can,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并等待最后的結果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and wait for the other shoe to drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.88,0:22:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太固執了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我更好的品質之一 但你似乎從不介意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not one of my better qualities. But you never seemed to mind.
