Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵循所有指示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Follow all instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出塞巴斯蒂安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deliver Sebastian now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要公正 交出塞巴斯蒂安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want justice. Deliver Sebastian now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在八公里外發現了一群僵尸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A swarm has been detected five miles out.
