Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.13,0:23:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clear the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.26,0:23:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再說一遍 在八公里外發現了一群僵尸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I repeat, a swarm has been detected five miles out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.09,0:23:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-離開這里 所有人 -好吧 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Clear out, everyone. - All right. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們勇敢的聯邦軍隊將在它們...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our brave Commonwealth Army will be intercepting it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:23:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 我們走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Let's go.
