Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.71,0:24:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.59,0:24:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擋路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.73,0:24:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到你們的家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Return to your homes.
