Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.86,0:24:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我們到底在尋找什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. What are we looking for exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.74,0:24:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍圖 示意圖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh... Blueprints, schematics.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.20,0:24:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合車站的計劃一定在這的某個地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Plans for Union Station have to be here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.78,0:25:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.25,0:25:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找的人在人們開始要他的腦袋前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The person that I'm looking for was in the building
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.04,0:25:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這棟大樓里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}right before people started calling for his head.
