Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.13,0:25:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.02,0:25:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我有告訴你我結婚了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, did I tell you I got married?
