Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.70,0:25:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她懷著我們的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and she is carrying our child.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.59,0:25:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.01,0:26:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-謝謝 -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - Yeah.
