Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.15,0:26:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道利亞對你來說很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that Leah meant something to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.78,0:27:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.78,0:27:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格倫會希望我照顧你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Glenn would've wanted me to look after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.83,0:27:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必說對不起 不必對我說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to ever say sorry. Not to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.67,0:27:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 發現什么了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. Hey. Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.38,0:27:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他帶了一半的人在前面搜尋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's dug in up ahead with half his men.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.05,0:27:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能靠近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We wouldn't get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.64,0:27:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人在從后面攻擊我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The others are flanking us from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.64,0:27:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該在他們把我們堵死之前往東走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should go east before they pin us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.27,0:27:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么辦法可以移向他們后面嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there any way to get behind them?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.60,0:27:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣會被他們發現的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not without them spotting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.73,0:27:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非他們看不到我們過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unless they never see us coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.83,0:27:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Come on, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.96,0:27:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go, go, go, go. Go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.05,0:28:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go, go, go. Go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.68,0:28:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 請幫個小忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello there. Small favor, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.77,0:28:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在出來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Coming out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.40,0:29:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們出發前的最后召集\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last call before we head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.15,0:29:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.28,0:29:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說有僵尸要殺 我無法抗拒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard walkers needed killing. I couldn't resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.95,0:29:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵尸已通過第二個檢查站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Swarm has passed the second checkpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.58,0:29:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們需要支援 -堅守位置 我們馬上到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We need support. - Hold your position. On our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.46,0:29:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Moving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.11,0:29:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你還好嗎  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You okay? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.57,0:29:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-只是...你知道 -是的 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Just... You know. - Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.87,0:29:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你想休息一下嗎  -不 我們應該繼續前進\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You want to take a minute? - No. We should keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.66,0:30:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們繼續朝這邊走 我們應該會追上他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we keep going that way, we should come up right behind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.67,0:30:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們可以讓他們到我們這里來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we can get them to come down here to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.40,0:31:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想這么說 但我們已經沒有可搜索的地方了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hate to say it, but we are running out of places to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.20,0:31:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看那個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me have a look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.96,0:31:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么了  -這里應該有一扇門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - Should be a door here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.67,0:32:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.18,0:32:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.60,0:32:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是怎么進來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How'd you guys get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.10,0:32:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-放松 伙計 -放開我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy, champ. Get them off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.52,0:32:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.99,0:32:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你知道我是誰嗎  -你知道我是誰嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you know who I am? - Oh. Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.49,0:32:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些混蛋想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you assholes want?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.91,0:32:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來 我們帶你回家見你媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get up. We're taking you home to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.92,0:32:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這件事結束之前 我不會去任何地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not going anywhere until this thing blows over.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.75,0:32:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-反正我媽媽也不在乎 -她在乎的 你是她的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- My mother doesn't care anyway. - Yes, she does. You're her kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.63,0:32:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦是她的孩子 我只是個麻煩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Commonwealth is her kid. I'm just a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.14,0:33:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.06,0:33:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 小子 當你拿罐子撒尿 每個人都想要你死的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Junior, when you're pissing in jars and everybody wants you dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.48,0:33:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能是瘋了 但我想也許是時候該 重新考慮你的選擇了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}call me nuts, but I think maybe it's time to rethink your options.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.11,0:33:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里的這位 她是個超級魔術師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, this one here, well, she's a goddamn magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.49,0:33:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我親眼見過她做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have seen her pull little bunnies right out of her ass
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.82,0:33:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with my very own two eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.78,0:33:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 如果 無論出于何種原因 她要救你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So if, for whatever reason, she is throwing you a life raft,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.91,0:33:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我建議你接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}well, then I recommend you jump in that sucker
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.12,0:33:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來解救自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and save yourself from drowning.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.09,0:33:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真覺得你能幫上忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You really think you can help?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.44,0:33:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停 你們違反了宵禁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop. You are in violation of curfew.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.11,0:34:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵尸已經過前兩個外部檢查站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The swarm is past the first two outer checkpoints.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.87,0:34:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to your homes immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.09,0:34:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的女兒永遠也不能回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My daughter can never return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.67,0:34:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到他們交出塞巴斯蒂安米爾頓 我們哪都不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we're not moving until Sebastian Milton is brought to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.80,0:34:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.81,0:34:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是亨德森 我們有情況\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Henderson. We have a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.08,0:34:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我找到他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. Hey. I found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.62,0:34:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到他了 塞巴斯蒂安在這里 他在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I found him. Sebastian's here. He's over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.33,0:34:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去吧 我會處理好這件事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You guys go. I'll take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.21,0:34:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弄錯人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ooh. You got the wrong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.42,0:34:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在這里 塞巴斯蒂安在這 他要跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's over here. Sebastian's here. He's getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.80,0:34:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弄錯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.47,0:35:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 我們走 抓住他 別讓他跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Let's go. Let's get him. Don't let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.10,0:35:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你們的最后警告 回家 在這里不安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is your final warning. Go home. You are not safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.32,0:35:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕梅拉撒謊 塞巴斯蒂安殺人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pamela lies. Sebastian kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.32,0:35:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這是為了你們自身的安全 -塞巴斯蒂安殺人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is for your own protection. - Sebastian kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.37,0:35:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 聽著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just shut the hell up and listen for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.60,0:35:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 干掉他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine. Clear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.36,0:36:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-它們通過了第三個檢查站 -處理它們 艾克 德爾塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They passed checkpoint three. Execute, Echo, Delta.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.54,0:37:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德爾塔隊 繼續向西移動 艾克在途中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Delta team, keep moving to the west. Echo is en route.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.34,0:37:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃斯皮諾薩和我會處理剩下的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Espinosa and I will handle what's left.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.05,0:37:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外圍發生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to the outer perimeter?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.34,0:37:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-僵尸是怎么到這么近的  -有人沒有做他們的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How did the walkers get this close? - Somebody wasn't doing their job.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.89,0:37:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里似乎發生了很多事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seems to happen a lot around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.89,0:37:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那周的事情...不應該發生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About the other week... That shouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.56,0:37:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我感謝你支持我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I appreciate you having my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.77,0:37:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你在盡你所能 我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. You're trying to do what you can. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.65,0:37:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 這里很混亂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Shit is upside-down around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.91,0:37:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這份工作中 我需要像你這樣的人 我可以信任的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In this job, I need people like you, people I can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.87,0:37:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能 對不起 如果你在這里需要我的幫助 我會幫你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't. I'm sorry. If you need my help out here, I'm your girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.84,0:37:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要我在社區幫你 我做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you want my help back there, that's not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.26,0:37:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女兒和家人永遠是第一位的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My daughter and my family will always come first.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.39,0:37:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尊重你的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.43,0:37:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果時機到了 你決定離開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the time comes and you decide to go
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.52,0:37:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要幫助 我會幫你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you need help getting out, I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.31,0:38:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是德爾塔 艾克倒下了 車輛翻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Delta. Echo is down. Vehicle overturned.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.32,0:38:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 來 干掉它們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch it. Come on. Take them out. Take them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.84,0:38:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.08,0:38:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的手給我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.49,0:38:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help me! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.85,0:39:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得走了 長官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}TROOPER 2: We got to go, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.57,0:40:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要一杯嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you like one?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.24,0:40:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說有點早 謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a little early for me. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.41,0:40:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我的朋友們用了催淚瓦斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You tear-gassed my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.04,0:40:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們在那 他們就是無視封鎖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If they were there, they were in defiance of lockdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.54,0:40:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么做有幫助嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And did it help?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.58,0:40:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這讓士兵在城外的工作更容易了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did it actually make the troopers' jobs easier outside the walls?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.21,0:40:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們所做的是為了防患可能發生的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was about what could have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.67,0:40:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了安全 一直如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was about safety. It always is.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.93,0:40:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在乎這會讓你看起來良心有愧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you don't care that it makes you look guilty?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.97,0:40:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有一個指控 由美子 就說出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you have an accusation, Yumiko, make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.36,0:40:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 你真的能坐在那里說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look. Can you really sit there and say there is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.82,0:40:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你兒子沒有做過他被指控的那些事嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no way your son did the things he was accused of?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.03,0:40:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直是個叛逆者 這是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's always been something of a renegade, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.24,0:41:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他的祖父和叔叔們也是這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But his grandfather and uncles were the same way,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.25,0:41:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時間的推移 他們逐漸成熟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and they mellowed over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.62,0:41:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為人們的領袖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Became leaders of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.75,0:41:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許他的青春叛逆比大多數人都晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe he's having his youthful rebellions later than most,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.46,0:41:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他不是個兇手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he's not a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.46,0:41:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕梅拉 我想弄清楚你知道多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pamela, I am trying to figure out how much you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.88,0:41:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護你可能是我的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It might be my job to defend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.26,0:41:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我的律師和這里最杰出的記者 也是朋友時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can I talk to my lawyer freely when she's also friends
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.47,0:41:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如何與她自由交談\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with the most prominent journalist around?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.53,0:41:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.21,0:41:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你羞辱了我和你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've humiliated me and yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.13,0:41:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴過你我不應該來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you I shouldn't have come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.84,0:41:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我 你和這一切有什么關系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at me. What did you have to do with all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.89,0:41:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.93,0:42:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 那個故事是謊言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look. That story is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.72,0:42:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們想要有人對此負責 而我很容易成為目標\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People, they want someone to blame and I'm an easy target.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.89,0:42:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要告訴我更多 我才能救你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll need to tell me more than that for me to save your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.81,0:42:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我們可以互相幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think we can help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.44,0:42:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你是誰  -我為蘭斯霍恩斯比工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And who are you? - I work for Lance Hornsby.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.49,0:42:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打著你的招牌在外面追捕我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's out there hunting my friends under your flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.49,0:42:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你的幫助來阻止他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need your help to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.24,0:42:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對此一無所知 而且我看不出 這如何能幫到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know anything about this. And I don't see how it helps me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.00,0:42:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你的兒子沒有做過他被指控的事情 那么就是別人做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If your son didn't do the things that he's accused of, someone did.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.09,0:43:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 一切到此結束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, this ends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.96,0:43:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下你的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drop your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.01,0:43:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把槍放下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guns on the ground. Guns on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.10,0:43:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-告訴他們 馬上 -放下武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Tell them, now. - TROOPER 2: Weapons down.
